{"tid":117892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肥到豬咁既老虎","createTime":"2017-02-12T14:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T16:40:00.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1a26402d829138b61304659aba757f7ec9c277","tid":117892,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/supplement/20170212/37549465/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Fappledaily%2Farticle%2Fsupplement%2F20170212%2F37549465%2F&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0e403152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/supplement/20170212/37549465/</a><br />\n根據網站Metro的報導，在中國哈爾濱市的「東北虎林園」裡，有一隻被過度餵食的東北虎，腫脹得像氣球般、病懨懨躺的牠只能在籠內徘徊度日，這樣的情況不只引起網友關注、也讓遊客十分擔心，但園方卻表示無須擔心，冬天本來就會讓老虎吃飽一點、儲存重量，這些多長的春天就會瘦下來。<br />\n但動保團體卻強力譴責，在如此不自然的飲食下、已經是過度肥胖了，且環境也極缺乏運動機會，讓牠瘦不下來。因人工飼養的老虎無法狩獵、導致儲存重量這件事變得非常沒必要。有網站爆料，「東北虎林園」販賣牛肉條及活體的雞給遊客，讓他們餵食這些東北虎，也是造成肥胖的主因之一，令人失望地、仍有許多遊客買單，過度餵食也是種動物虐待，希望民眾了解到這樣的事實、讓這些老虎回到原本的體態。（廖家葆╱綜合報導）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zb3523H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZb3523H.jpg&h=7565be2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44489367a1d7ab69f4ad02a91d215183de352ca0","tid":117892,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:30:51.000Z","msg":"屌你仲話冬天儲肥啲係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那人真係完全冇廉恥"},{"pid":"3733a918362131da569b60714180c68674e8bd04","tid":117892,"uid":52927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"好得意"},{"pid":"d450550e57cb4c047481aa409a18314f600bcfec","tid":117892,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"以前荔園隻象都係靠遊客買蕉餵食， 但瘦到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7974600944abba401cbc3d48dcfc14c82780ed35","tid":117892,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"你困撚住佢已經係動物虐待啦<br />\n人類真係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a5c5fad9635960598ed8aba984f31d0de2c7fe","tid":117892,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}